{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_197-364_0342_jenie.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.722, "text": "Seventeen, no, eighteen days ago."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_197-364_0252_jenie.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.8842, "text": "O'Brien had been a clean living young man with ideals."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_197-364_0305_jenie.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 5.4682, "text": "They had no fixed values, to be altered by adjectives and adverbs."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/Neutral_1-28_0004_bea.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.5441, "text": "Lord, but I'm glad to see you again, Phil."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_141-168_0142_bea.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.9453, "text": "Such things had occurred before, he told Philip."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_141_168_0145_bea.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 4.1085, "text": "I have to be careful of them as they tear very easily."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_281-308_0290_bea.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 2.642, "text": "One by one the boys were captured,"}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/OAF_wash_sad.wav", "emotion": "sad", "duration": 2.5798, "text": "Say the word wash."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/Neutral_85-112_0101_bea.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.2964, "text": "You you would not keep the truth from me."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/YAF_met_happy.wav", "emotion": "happy", "duration": 1.8148, "text": "Say the word meant."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/OAF_hush_happy.wav", "emotion": "happy", "duration": 1.8888, "text": "Say the word hush."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_197-224_0217_josh.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 4.6661, "text": "Oppressive as the heat had been, it was now even more oppressive."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/OAF_third_angry.wav", "emotion": "angry", "duration": 1.378, "text": "Say the word third."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_393-420_0398_sam.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 9.4904, "text": "In the car were Unwind and Harrison, while Jones sat with the chauffeur."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_57-84_0072_sam.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 2.7485, "text": "But who is Aileen's double?"}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/OAF_moon_sad.wav", "emotion": "sad", "duration": 2.6028, "text": "Say the word moon."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_57-84_0084_josh.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.8158, "text": "Scarcely had he uttered the name when Pierre's closing eyes shot open."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_393-420_0415_sam.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.1148, "text": "It lasted as a deterrent for two days."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/OAF_when_sad.wav", "emotion": "sad", "duration": 2.3461, "text": "Say the word when."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_57-84_0077_josh.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 2.842, "text": "It is the fire, partly, she said."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_197-224_0209_josh.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 2.8445, "text": "It was not a large lake, and almost round."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_46-56_0055_bea.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 5.8367, "text": "Philip stood undecided, his ears strained to catch the slightest sound."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/OAF_book_neutral.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 1.7331, "text": "Say the word book."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_169-196_0171_jenie.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 5.0602, "text": "And when you come back in a few days, bring Aileen."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_169-196_0186_sam.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 4.0336, "text": "Like a flash he launched himself into the feathered mass of the owl."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_197-364_0346_jenie.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 2.842, "text": "Get down and dig in."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_1-28_0002_jenie.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 5.048, "text": "Not at this particular case, Tom, apologized Whitmore."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_141-168_0162_josh.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.603, "text": "That's the sub foreman, explained Thorpe."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_253-280_0276_bea.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 5.1388, "text": "Ulangatoll was 140 miles in circumference."}
