{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/OAF_tough_neutral.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 1.9097, "text": "Say the word tough."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_85-112_0110_josh.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.9941, "text": "Much, replied Jean, as tersely."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_113-140_0114_bea.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 4.1781, "text": "Her words sent a strange chill through Philip."}
