{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_197-364_0319_jenie.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 4.2283, "text": "And the Edinburgh Evening News says with editorial gloom"}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_365-392_0373_jenie.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.3888, "text": "Points of view, new ideas, life."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_225-252_0237_bea.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.6088, "text": "So Huey and I did the managing ourselves."}
