{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_197-224_0224_bea.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.8784, "text": "She nodded, and her eyes grew soft and moist."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/OAF_love_happy.wav", "emotion": "happy", "duration": 2.0659, "text": "Say the word love."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_169-196_0185_bea.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.8115, "text": "The questions may have come vaguely in his mind."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_27-56_0045_josh.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 4.3744, "text": "He moved away as quietly as he had come."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_367-392_0377_sam.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 4.2388, "text": "This sound did not disturb the hush and awe of the place."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/Neutral_57-84_0076_bea.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 4.3271, "text": "The gray eyes faltered, the flush deepened."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_281-308_0294_sam.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 4.8558, "text": "He had been foiled in his attempt to escape."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_27-56_0052_josh.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 3.8341, "text": "It was a curious coincidence."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_169-196_0176_bea.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.4772, "text": "For the first time in his life he was yearning for a scrap,"}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/YAF_wire_sad.wav", "emotion": "sad", "duration": 2.4595, "text": "Say the word wire."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_196-224_0212_bea.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 4.8542, "text": "Fresh gazes still able to walk, they clustered about the spokesman."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_281-308_0294_josh.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 2.6571, "text": "He had been foiled in his attempt to escape."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_29-56_0037_sam.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.3585, "text": "I was the only one who remained sitting."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_29-56_0033_sam.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 5.1777, "text": "He unfolded a long typewritten letter, and handed it to Dredson."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_393-420_0396_sam.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.1816, "text": "A rising tide of fat had submerged them."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/YAF_goal_happy.wav", "emotion": "happy", "duration": 1.8407, "text": "Say the word goal."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_141-168_0161_bea.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.8221, "text": "Take away their foremen, and they wouldn't be worth their grub."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/YAF_near_happy.wav", "emotion": "happy", "duration": 1.896, "text": "Say the word near."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_197_224_0221_sam.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 1.9044, "text": "I don't know why you're here at all."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/YAF_thumb_sad.wav", "emotion": "sad", "duration": 2.1586, "text": "Say the word thumb."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_225-252_0244_bea.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 4.5706, "text": "He was the soul of devotion to his employers,"}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/OAF_death_sad.wav", "emotion": "sad", "duration": 2.4852, "text": "Say the word death."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/YAF_said_happy.wav", "emotion": "happy", "duration": 1.8885, "text": "Say the word said."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/OAF_peg_sad.wav", "emotion": "sad", "duration": 2.597, "text": "Say the word peg."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/YAF_nag_angry.wav", "emotion": "angry", "duration": 2.0895, "text": "Say the word nag."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/OAF_jar_happy.wav", "emotion": "happy", "duration": 1.925, "text": "Say the word jar."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_85-112_0087_josh.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 4.03, "text": "Philip bent lower and stared into the face of the dead man."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_281-308_0283_josh.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 4.9158, "text": "The woman in you is only incidental, accidental, and irrelevant."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_1-28_0003_josh.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 4.2288, "text": "For the twentieth time that evening the two men shook hands."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_29-45_0034_bea.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 4.2425, "text": "Men of Seldom's stamp don't stop at women and children."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/YAF_third_angry.wav", "emotion": "angry", "duration": 2.2085, "text": "Say the word third."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_1-28_0022_jenie.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 7.5298, "text": "Hardly were our plans made public before we were met by powerful opposition."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/YAF_dodge_happy.wav", "emotion": "happy", "duration": 1.9836, "text": "Say the word dodge."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/YAF_said_sad.wav", "emotion": "sad", "duration": 2.2495, "text": "Say the word said."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_252-280_0270_josh.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 4.2729, "text": "And after the bath, the shave would not be bad."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_336-364_0352_sam.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.9266, "text": "I'm sure going along with you all, Elijah."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_281-308_0281_josh.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 4.1056, "text": "I do not blame you for anything. Remember that."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_113-140_0140_josh.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 4.8542, "text": "Accept the Father's blessing, and with it, this."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/neutral_57-84_0071_sam.wav", "emotion": "neutral", "duration": 3.3131, "text": "What was the outject of your little sensation?"}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_57-84_0064_bea.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 4.071, "text": "The fourth and fifth days passed without any developments."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_85-112_0104_sam.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 6.9048, "text": "She was sleeping under his protection as sweetly as a child."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/dzejn/Documents/all-datasets/amused_57-84_0067_bea.wav", "emotion": "amused", "duration": 4.2477, "text": "Surely I will excuse you she cried."}
